
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>İletişim — Hesap Kimde?</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="icon.png">
<style>
  :root{--ink:#0b0b16;--panel:#171733;--panel-2:#1e1e40;--gold:#FFC93C;--gold-deep:#F0A500;--coral:#FF5D73;--violet:#8B6DFF;--mint:#3DDC97;--text:#EDECFF;--text-dim:#9E9CC8;--line:rgba(255,255,255,.09)}
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  body{background:var(--ink);color:var(--text);font-family:'Trebuchet MS','Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  body::before{content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;background:radial-gradient(420px 320px at 12% 8%,rgba(255,93,115,.16),transparent 70%),radial-gradient(460px 360px at 88% 4%,rgba(139,109,255,.18),transparent 70%),radial-gradient(520px 420px at 50% 100%,rgba(61,220,151,.09),transparent 70%)}
  header,main,footer{position:relative;z-index:1}
  .wrap{max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px;width:100%}
  header{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:60;background:rgba(11,11,22,.72);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  .nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:62px;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px}
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:800;font-size:17px;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none}
  .brand img{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px}
  .lang{display:flex;gap:3px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;padding:3px}
  .lang button{border:none;background:transparent;color:var(--text-dim);font-weight:800;font-size:12px;padding:6px 13px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}
  .lang button.active{background:var(--gold);color:var(--ink)}
  main{flex:1;padding:60px 0 70px;text-align:center}
  h1{font-size:clamp(30px,6vw,46px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.8px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .sub{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:16px;max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 40px}
  .card{background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--panel),var(--panel-2));border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:22px;padding:36px 28px;margin-bottom:18px;transition:transform .18s,border-color .18s}
  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:rgba(255,201,60,.35)}
  .card .ic{width:60px;height:60px;margin:0 auto 16px;border-radius:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:29px;background:rgba(255,201,60,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,201,60,.3)}
  .card h2{font-size:19px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:6px}
  .card p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:18px}
  .btn{display:inline-block;text-decoration:none;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink);background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-deep));padding:12px 26px;border-radius:12px;transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s}
  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 26px rgba(255,201,60,.3)}
  .mail{font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:18px;display:block}
  .stores{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px}
  .store{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none;background:var(--text);color:var(--ink);padding:11px 18px;border-radius:12px;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;transition:transform .15s}
  .store:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .store svg{width:20px;height:20px}
  .back{display:inline-block;margin-top:34px;color:var(--text-dim);text-decoration:none;font-weight:700}
  .back:hover{color:var(--gold)}
  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:26px 0;text-align:center;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-dim);opacity:.7}
  html[lang="tr"] [data-en]{display:none !important}
  html[lang="en"] [data-tr]{display:none !important}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="nav">
    <a class="brand" href="index.html"><img src="icon.png" alt=""><span data-tr>Hesap Kimde?</span><span data-en>Who Pays?</span></a>
    <div class="lang">
      <button id="btn-tr" class="active" onclick="setLang('tr')">TR</button>
      <button id="btn-en" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1 data-tr>İletişim</h1>
    <h1 data-en>Contact</h1>
    <p class="sub" data-tr>Soru, öneri ya da geri bildirimin mi var? Bize yaz — okumaktan mutluluk duyarız!</p>
    <p class="sub" data-en>Got a question, suggestion, or feedback? Drop us a line — we'd love to hear from you!</p>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="ic">✉️</div>
      <h2 data-tr>Bize ulaş</h2>
      <h2 data-en>Reach us</h2>
      <p data-tr>Her konuda tek adres:</p>
      <p data-en>One address for everything:</p>
      <span class="mail">info@hesapkimde.app</span>
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:info@hesapkimde.app" data-tr>E-posta gönder</a>
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:info@hesapkimde.app" data-en>Send an email</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="ic">📱</div>
      <h2 data-tr>Uygulamayı indir</h2>
      <h2 data-en>Get the app</h2>
      <p data-tr>Değerlendirme ve yorumlarını mağazalardan da paylaşabilirsin.</p>
      <p data-en>You can also share your ratings and reviews on the stores.</p>
      <div class="stores">
        <a class="store" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hakozi.hesapkimde" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 2.5c-.3.2-.5.6-.5 1.1v16.8c0 .5.2.9.5 1.1l9.3-9.5L3 2.5z" fill="#22c55e"/><path d="M16.5 8.2L4.6 1.5C4.2 1.3 3.8 1.3 3.5 1.5l9.1 9.3 3.9-2.6z" fill="#FFC93C"/><path d="M20.3 10.4l-3.8-2.2-4 4.1 4 4 3.8-2.2c.8-.5.8-1.7 0-2.2v-1.5z" fill="#FF5D73"/><path d="M3.5 22.5c.3.2.7.2 1.1 0l11.9-6.7-3.9-2.6-9.1 9.3z" fill="#8B6DFF"/></svg>
          Google Play
        </a>
        <a class="store" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6781272465" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16.4 12.6c0-2.3 1.9-3.4 2-3.5-1.1-1.6-2.8-1.8-3.4-1.8-1.4-.1-2.8.9-3.5.9-.7 0-1.8-.8-3-.8-1.5 0-2.9.9-3.7 2.3-1.6 2.7-.4 6.8 1.1 9 .7 1.1 1.6 2.3 2.7 2.2 1.1 0 1.5-.7 2.8-.7 1.3 0 1.6.7 2.8.7 1.2 0 1.9-1.1 2.6-2.2.8-1.2 1.2-2.4 1.2-2.5-.1 0-2.3-.9-2.3-3.5z M14.2 5.6c.6-.7 1-1.7.9-2.7-.9 0-1.9.6-2.5 1.3-.6.6-1.1 1.6-.9 2.6 1 .1 2-.5 2.5-1.2z"/></svg>
          App Store
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="ic">📷</div>
      <h2 data-tr>Instagram'da takip et</h2>
      <h2 data-en>Follow on Instagram</h2>
      <p data-tr>Yenilikler ve perde arkası için:</p>
      <p data-en>For updates and behind the scenes:</p>
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.instagram.com/hakancivak/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@hakancivak</a>
    </div>

    <a class="back" href="index.html" data-tr>← Ana sayfaya dön</a>
    <a class="back" href="index.html" data-en>← Back to home</a>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <span data-tr>© 2026 Hesap Kimde? · Hakozi</span>
  <span data-en>© 2026 Who Pays? · Hakozi</span>
</footer>

<script>
  function setLang(l){
    document.documentElement.lang=l;
    document.getElementById('btn-tr').classList.toggle('active',l==='tr');
    document.getElementById('btn-en').classList.toggle('active',l==='en');
    document.title = l==='en' ? 'Contact — Who Pays?' : 'İletişim — Hesap Kimde?';
    try{localStorage.setItem('hk-lang',l)}catch(e){}
  }
  (function(){
    var s;try{s=localStorage.getItem('hk-lang')}catch(e){}
    var n=(navigator.language||'tr').slice(0,2);
    setLang(s||(n==='en'?'en':'tr'));
  })();
</script>
</body>
</html>
